{
  "stem": "5810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother certainly was not in-- although she reminded me on a daily basis when I did go to Catholic school, never to forget that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to-- to forget it at the hours that I was in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was kind of-- kind of a mixture of trying to remember I was a Jew, and at the same time I was to forget it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Otherwise it meant my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I lost my train of thought.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I hope you'll forgive me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a teacher in the class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in those days, for all-- well, I think still today I guess, in elementary school, which is what it was, the-- the teacher was the same teacher all day long.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't a change of teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They taught all the subjects.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I guess I must have been told by the principal, or must have known, or must have suspected something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I felt very close to this teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he always showed an interest in me, and a liking to me and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember one time where there was a search that had not been announced.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we heard the German troops going from classes to classes to classes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were one of the last ones that they were going to walk into.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, oh my god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is where they're going to discover me and I have to trust someone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went over to that teacher and I told him straight out-- I had no choice at that point-- I told them that I was Jewish and he seemed to already know it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And could he do something for me?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
